果和经验面撰写的一部专著，", "box": [[62.0, 95.0], [525.0, 97.0], [525.0, 113.0], [62.0, 110.0]], "x0": 62.0, "y0": 95.0, "x1": 525.0, "y1": 113.0, "center_x": 293.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9875, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 1}, {"text": "详细、全面并理论联系实际地阐述了燃烧室设计和研发各方面的技术问题，包括燃烧室气体动力学、燃油喷射雾", "box": [[41.0, 111.0], [526.0, 113.0], [526.0, 128.0], [41.0, 126.0]], "x0": 41.0, "y0": 111.0, "x1": 526.0, "y1": 128.0, "center_x": 283.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9816, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 2}, {"text": "化、燃油蒸发、液雾穿透、油气混合、燃烧效率、点火、火焰稳定、总压损失、出口温度分布、冷却、污染排放、", "box": [[41.0, 127.0], [525.0, 129.0], [525.0, 143.0], [41.0, 141.0]], "x0": 41.0, "y0": 127.0, "x1": 525.0, "y1": 143.0, "center_x": 283.0, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9754, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 3}, {"text": "噪声、自燃与同火，以及燃油沉积等方面的内容。本书完全针对以低污染燃烧室和高温升燃烧室为代表的新一代先", "box": [[41.0, 142.0], [526.0, 144.0], [526.0, 158.0], [40.0, 156.0]], "x0": 40.0, "y0": 142.0, "x1": 526.0, "y1": 158.0, "center_x": 283.0, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9875, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 4}, {"text": "进燃烧室设计研发的需要而撰写，是我国自行设计研发先进燃烧室的基础。", "box": [[41.0, 159.0], [353.0, 160.0], [353.0, 173.0], [40.0, 172.0]], "x0": 40.0, "y0": 159.0, "x1": 353.0, "y1": 173.0, "center_x": 196.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9698, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 5}, {"text": "本书内容丰富，立足21世纪先进燃烧室技术，大部分是作者自己科研、设计和研发的实践总结，这是本书与", "box": [[61.0, 174.0], [526.0, 176.0], [526.0, 189.0], [61.0, 188.0]], "x0": 61.0, "y0": 174.0, "x1": 526.0, "y1": 189.0, "center_x": 293.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9738, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 6}, {"text": "其他类似出版物最大的区别。本书适合于从事燃气涡轮发动机燃烧室设计研发人员和研究生使用，也可作为相关专", "box": [[41.0, 189.0], [526.0, 191.0], [526.0, 205.0], [41.0, 203.0]], "x0": 41.0, "y0": 189.0, "x1": 526.0, "y1": 205.0, "center_x": 283.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9936, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 7}, {"text": "业科技人员和高等院校师生参考用书。", "box": [[42.0, 206.0], [199.0, 206.0], [199.0, 219.0], [42.0, 219.0]], "x0": 42.0, "y0": 206.0, "x1": 199.0, "y1": 219.0, "center_x": 120.5, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 0.9782, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 8}, {"text": "图书在版编目（CIP）数据", "box": [[62.0, 321.0], [228.0, 321.0], [228.0, 338.0], [62.0, 337.0]], "x0": 62.0, "y0": 321.0, "x1": 228.0, "y1": 338.0, "center_x": 145.0, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 0.9969, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 9}, {"text": "先进燃气轮机燃烧室/金如山，索建秦著.--北京：", "box": [[66.0, 351.0], [361.0, 354.0], [361.0, 370.0], [66.0, 368.0]], "x0": 66.0, "y0": 351.0, "x1": 361.0, "y1": 370.0, "center_x": 213.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9599, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 10}, {"text": "航空工业出版社，2016.8", "box": [[41.0, 371.0], [182.0, 373.0], [182.0, 388.0], [40.0, 386.0]], "x0": 40.0, "y0": 371.0, "x1": 182.0, "y1": 388.0, "center_x": 111.0, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 0.9988, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 11}, {"text": "航空发动机出版工程", "box": [[66.0, 390.0], [183.0, 390.0], [183.0, 406.0], [66.0, 406.0]], "x0": 66.0, "y0": 390.0, "x1": 183.0, "y1": 406.0, "center_x": 124.5, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 1.0, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 12}, {"text": "ISBN 978 7  5165 1086 5", "box": [[64.0, 409.0], [231.0, 410.0], [231.0, 426.0], [64.0, 425.0]], "x0": 64.0, "y0": 409.0, "x1": 231.0, "y1": 426.0, "center_x": 147.5, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 0.954, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 13}, {"text": "1.①先.ⅡI.①金.…②索.Ⅲ.①航空发动机", "box": [[67.0, 434.0], [364.0, 435.0], [364.0, 451.0], [67.0, 450.0]], "x0": 67.0, "y0": 434.0, "x1": 364.0, "y1": 451.0, "center_x": 215.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.7656, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 14}, {"text": "燃气轮机一燃烧室IⅣV.①V23